        <updateDate>2008-07-22T18:39:58Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Responsible Investment for Home Ownership Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) establish tax-exempt Home Ownership Mortgage Expense Accounts; (2) allow a tax deduction for contributions to such accounts; (3) allow tax-free distributions from such accounts for the financing or remodeling of a principal residence; and (4) set forth rules for such accounts relating to prohibited transactions, rollover contributions, and account termination. Prohibits illegal aliens making tax deductible contributions to such accounts. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>Responsible Investment for Home Ownership Act of 2008</title>
